ActEmergency Management Act
SubjectNo. 128 - (Ontario) Provincial Emergencies Financial Assistance Order
PrecisPROVINCIAL EMERGENCY FINANCIAL ASSISTANCE ORDER NO. 128 - which makes a declaration of federal concern and authorizes the federal government to provide financial assistance to the province of ONTARIO with respect to the arrival at the Ottawa and Montreal international airports of repatriated victims living and deceased of the earthquake which affected HAITI on January 12, 2010 and who required support from the province between January 13 and March 31, 2010.
